rows.label: qst701109_msg0001
rows.name:
I owe the old master a lot from back in
the day. He saved me when I was down
and out after I made some bad choices.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0002
rows.name:
He was always upfront with me. Angry
when he had to be, but always for good
reason. He asked for nothing back.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd decided back then that whenever he
needed me, I'd do anything for him.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0004
rows.name:
That's why I knew what I had to do,
though I don't much care for Wotta and
his harebrained, goody-two-shoes deal.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0005
rows.name:
It does, on the other hand, make him
a great patsy if anything goes wrong...
Uh, don't tell Arb I said that, OK?
